        <briefdescription>
<para>Computes Hankel transform, using digital filters. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Corresponds to strategies 6-11 in SASfit. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Does not allow any error control. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Perform wells for simple form factors, but it does struggle with oscillatory ones. For oscillatory form factors, it is advisable to start with this method for a rough Hankel transform computation, and then refine it with &quot;hankel_transform_QWE_Chave&quot; or &quot;hankel_transform_QWE_Key&quot;.</para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
